h1. execOutsideUI{}

h2. Purpose

Executes a block of code outside of the UI Thread.

h2. Examples

{code:java}
class SampleController {
    def action = { evt = null ->
        execOutsideUI {
            // long running computation
        }
    }
}
{code}

h2. Description

See the [threading|guide:threading] section for more information about this method and others like it.
